{
  "id": "RAW_b29b363b",
  "title": "前端开发最大短板，这次终于补上了！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536528&idx=1&sn=8aba060b4ce5db2d1dd682214a97a19f",
  "date": "2025-12-16 01:01:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cec553f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMMgIicuFdBiaSfIzqFesgIb1bBfFOMvQ6ISKQ8NOz9BNlGsusPocgtIhEN49Ribz1HhrwS1CfLllOVvQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"前端充电宝\" data-alias=\"FE-Charge\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EO58xpw5UMNJLOYUj7Uv3TSiaqDldeaxxhCosR00yDKGR9lvI4y9NOfG7ADJHfKEsKuVAFWgDPqLN5afgZGkbZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"聚焦前端开发，探索AI新浪潮：宝藏工具×前沿动态×实战技巧，解锁前端新可能！\" data-id=\"MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在折腾自己的项目时，遇到一个特别让人抓狂的问题：我需要一整套风格统一的 App 设计稿，可我又完全不会做设计。于是只能依赖各种 AI 工具来辅助。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果试了一大圈，不是 UI 丑，就是风格混乱，要么画得像 PPT，要么像课程作业……越用越崩溃。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">直到我试了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">UXbot</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——我第一次觉得：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">原来 AI 做设计，可以做到专业团队级别。</span></strong></p>\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100052853\" data-ratio=\"0.7148148148148148\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0;display: block;width: auto;height: auto;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=001681d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMMgIicuFdBiaSfIzqFesgIb1bicchmYl1bLo9oicVzGcwomXibnITEuRxpfPgTGwIWNOAVnHLNib0j6R9icw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">先说结论</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">UXbot 是我目前见过最能用的 AI 设计工具。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么我会说它是“能用的”？因为它不是那种只给你整一张好看的单页、拿来当个参考就结束了的工具，而是能把整个产品从&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">流程 → 结构 → 页面 → 交互</span></strong><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">→ 代码</span></strong><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">→ 部署</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;一口气走下来。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以把它理解为一个“多合一”的工作流工具包：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个随叫随到、能帮你拆需求的产品经理</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个审美在线、风格稳定的设计师</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个能跑流程的原型工具</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个写得出可维护代码的前端</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">外加一键就能跑在云端的部署流程</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程体验下来，我的核心感受有四个：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">风格统一，不会越做越跑偏</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">不是死图，而是完整流程可实际操作</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑灵活，可以做到真正的产品级别</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">代码规范，生成后直接能跑</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面我就按照我的真实使用过程，一步步聊聊它到底能做到什么、适不适合前端用。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接上手</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了测试它到底行不行，我选了一个真实需求：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><span leaf=\"\">做一个</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">自媒体博主广告档期管理系统</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，包含完整的视觉设计 + 交互原型。</span></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我只输入了一段需求描述，它就开始自动分析，然后输出了一整套产品流程图。</span></p>\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100052855\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0;display: block;width: auto;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fba8a91a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMMgIicuFdBiaSfIzqFesgIb1bB1hzn32hGdwPicAWsmgTm4NaE3t4gGhBUYFtvEUEDf5S0vLJNyf9HhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UXbot 会把你的需求拆成：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">这类 App 理论上需要哪些模块？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个模块需要哪些页面？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个页面的核心功能是什么？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">页面之间如何跳？</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">市面上大多数 AI 工具生成 UI 的步骤是：“我给你一张好看的图，祝你好运。”</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 UXbot 把整个流程串起来，这种“有上下文、有结构、有完整故事线”的方式，这点超级像一个靠谱的产品经理。</span></p>\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些流程图都是可以编辑的，如果有不满意的地方，随时修改！</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">一键生成完整页面</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">流程图确认后，我让它开始画页面。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">几分钟之后，</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">24 个页面一次性生成完毕</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而且风格异常统一：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">主色调</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">组件样式</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">间距规范</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">图标风格</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">字体大小</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">交互结构</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">都非常一致，完全不像那种“AI 灵感乱飞”的画风。</span></p>\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100052857\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;mar